welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Jacinto City, the charming and vibrant city known for its rich history and friendly locals. We invite you to explore our cultural landmarks, delicious cuisine, and lively atmosphere. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at William P Hobby Airport handles all domestic flights and includes a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: International Terminal
terminals.description: The international terminal at William P Hobby Airport handles all international flights and includes customs and immigration facilities for travelers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at David Wayne Hooks Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at David Wayne Hooks Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Ellington Field Airport serves both commercial and general aviation flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is dedicated to private and charter flights at Ellington Field Airport.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Baytown Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers, including dining options, duty-free shopping, and comfortable waiting areas.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Baytown Airport caters to private and corporate jets, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience for its passengers.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
